# Project Rules

Canonical spec: [docs/MASTER_CONTEXT.md](docs/MASTER_CONTEXT.md)

## Stack

- Frontend: React 18, Vite, TS, React Router, TanStack Query, React Hook Form, Zod, Tailwind
- Backend: Express, TypeScript, Prisma, PostgreSQL
- Auth: JWT httpOnly cookie + RBAC (CLIENT | MANAGER)

## Architecture

Controller → Service → Repository → Prisma → PostgreSQL

Never access Prisma from controllers. Business logic in services only.

